://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tapestry will be displayed on the Hotel de la Marine in the Place de la Concorde in the French capital from late June.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_la_Marine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hotel de la Marine\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_la_Marine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_la_Marine\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999809006, \"rank\": 1.9005105192386548e-11, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.739859576475966, \"rank\": 0.306072879088447, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The installation will then be moved to Nice, home of the 2030 Winter Games, after the Paralympics concludes in September.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"score\": 0.9999887404769169, \"rank\": 1.122654410104701e-05, \"text\": \"Nice\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"